of solving their puzzle.

00:35:48.130 --> 00:35:51.100 align:middle line:84%
Anytime we solve a puzzle,
we have four corner pieces.

00:35:51.100 --> 00:35:53.800 align:middle line:84%
And they're the
same for everyone--

00:35:53.800 --> 00:35:59.840 align:middle line:84%
genetics, your digestive health,
your level of toxic exposure

00:35:59.840 --> 00:36:04.750 align:middle line:84%
including your thoughts,
and how willing and able

00:36:04.750 --> 00:36:08.300 align:middle line:90%
you are to detox those.

00:36:08.300 --> 00:36:11.320 align:middle line:84%
And then the last one is past
trauma and current-day stress.

00:36:11.320 --> 00:36:13.480 align:middle line:84%
So you asked earlier
if adult trauma

00:36:13.480 --> 00:36:15.850 align:middle line:90%
can cause this-- absolutely.

00:36:15.850 --> 00:36:19.090 align:middle line:84%
This can up-regulate your
genetic expression, too.

00:36:19.090 --> 00:36:21.420 align:middle line:84%
So for 23 years,
I haven't had RA.

00:36:21.420 --> 00:36:23.080 align:middle line:90%
I still have that gene.

00:36:23.080 --> 00:36:24.030 align:middle line:90%
My grandfather had.

00:36:24.030 --> 00:36:25.690 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You deactivated it.

00:36:25.690 --> 00:36:26.560 align:middle line:90%
You literally did.

00:36:26.560 --> 00:36:28.270 align:middle line:84%
>>EWERS: I changed
the way it manifests.

00:36:28.270 --> 00:36:28.900 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's amazing.

00:36:28.900 --> 00:36:31.400 align:middle line:84%
>>EWERS: So I do genetic testing
on every one of my patients

00:36:31.400 --> 00:36:32.510 align:middle line:90%
