childhood experiences.

00:37:58.090 --> 00:38:00.070 align:middle line:84%
And they impact your
health and the quality

00:38:00.070 --> 00:38:02.770 align:middle line:84%
of your relationships depending
on what you started believing

00:38:02.770 --> 00:38:05.620 align:middle line:90%
about them at that time.

00:38:05.620 --> 00:38:09.273 align:middle line:10%
C, connect the dots between
those beliefs, the behaviors

00:38:09.273 --> 00:38:10.690 align:middle line:10%
that emerged from
them, and what's

00:38:10.690 --> 00:38:13.930 align:middle line:10%
on the end of your fork,
how you're processing

