00:38:35.580 --> 00:38:38.760 align:middle line:84%
I call them the weight,
the resistance training

00:38:38.760 --> 00:38:41.670 align:middle line:90%
in your spiritual gymnasium.

00:38:41.670 --> 00:38:47.520 align:middle line:84%
They made me stronger, more
resilient, more compassionate,

00:38:47.520 --> 00:38:53.980 align:middle line:84%
a better mother, wife, healer,
coach, guide, and entrepreneur.

00:38:53.980 --> 00:38:59.120 align:middle line:10%
You are not a victim,
unless you choose it.

00:38:59.120 --> 00:39:02.240 align:middle line:84%
You have to reframe your
story to reclaim your health,

00:39:02.240 --> 00:39:04.580 align:middle line:84%
because you're the
superhero of your own life!

