spotting is another one

00:52:46.507 --> 00:52:48.090 align:middle line:84%
that a lot of people
haven't heard of.

00:52:48.090 --> 00:52:49.010 align:middle line:90%
That's a good one, too.

00:52:49.010 --> 00:52:49.885 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What is that?

00:52:49.885 --> 00:52:51.860 align:middle line:84%
>>EWERS: Brain
spotting was developed

00:52:51.860 --> 00:52:55.940 align:middle line:84%
