00:53:01.640 --> 00:53:02.330 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Huh, brain spotting.

00:53:02.330 --> 00:53:03.650 align:middle line:84%
>>EWERS: And people are
really worried about

00:53:03.650 --> 00:53:05.025 align:middle line:84%
