00:53:08.340 --> 00:53:09.620 align:middle line:90%
And that's not accurate.

00:53:09.620 --> 00:53:10.790 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It's releasing it.

00:53:10.790 --> 00:53:12.770 align:middle line:84%
>>EWERS: It's
rewiring your brain,

00:53:12.770 --> 00:53:15.710 align:middle line:84%
getting a nice bridge between
your adult brain and your child

00:53:15.710 --> 00:53:18.390 align:middle line:90%
brain, reframing.

00:53:18.390 --> 00:53:21.290 align:middle line:84%
It's a whole trauma
release piece.

00:53:21.290 --> 00:53:23.870 align:middle line:84%
And that doesn't happen
with talk therapy.

00:53:23.870 --> 00:53:25.310 align:middle line:84%
So yeah, the You
Unbroken program

00:53:25.310 --> 00:53:27.440 align:middle line:90%
